snippet.title: Soft Porn II: DOS Gaming
snippet.description:
We played a game called Softporn II, we tried it out for science. Only science, and it's pretty much what you'd expect from a DOS game called Softporn II. Enjoy (but not too much).

Check us out on SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/incredible-melting-men/timm-reads-episode-1
